# Bun install artifacts: in-parent-dir subpath symlinks for nested children packages
# (源真身在 <parent>/children/<child>/；这些 <parent>/<child> 软链由 bun install 生成且
#  目标相对深度有 bug；bun 运行时按 lockfile workspace 映射解析、不依赖它们，故整体忽略)
